Project Name : Chatlog

Objective : 
	To develop an online chat portal and store the messages in the database

Technology Used :
	Visual Studio Code
	Node Js
	Express JS
	socket.io
	Mongo Db

Description:
	To create a simple chat application. The front page is to login with and name and the room that the user wish to join. 
	All users in the single room name will be able to communicate with each other. 
	The users in the same room  will be notified as soon as the user joins and leaves the room.	
	The connection between different clients are made through socket.io
	Finally the user details, room name and the chat are stored in the mongo db.

npm run dev --> command to run the chat app
The server runs in the port 3000

